Face card flawless like my diamonds 💎

Steps to insure your jewelry:

1. Contact my insurance agency. ☎️ 678.981.3499
2. Make sure you have your appraisals.

4. Start a policy once your appraisals are completed.

- your favorite insurance agent

node.text: It’s so sad and crazy that you can let your family, your first cousin, live with you , take care of them, give them a job, let them drive your car, wear your clothes, feed them, wear your designer stuff, but they want to STEAL from you. I’m such a giving person, but I refuse to let even FAMILY take advantage of me. Never spent a penny when u was living with me, and this how u repay me! I’m not even mad, just disappointed! Since you want to block my numbers because you don’t want to return my designer bags, I’m calling the police and filing a police report. I’ve never been into taking business to Social media but if this how you wanna play dirty after I have opened up my whole world to you, so be it. Everyone leave a comment on her page to return my designer bags!!! chu_foo chu_foo chu_foo chu_foo
